ExpectationFeedback_2: The overall experience has been excellent, and in my opinion, the autonomous car is highly reliable. However, one aspect that stands out in this simulation is the absence of 'unpredictability,' a factor that plays a significant role in real-life scenarios. In reality, people and cars occasionally exhibit unpredictable behaviors, which the simulation may not fully capture. Incorporating more dynamic and unpredictable elements into the simulation could provide a more comprehensive testing environment and help prepare the autonomous car for the challenges it may face in the real world. Nonetheless, the system's reliability is certainly a reassuring aspect of this technology.
Interactivity_1: Introduce controlled elements of unpredictability to mimic real-world scenarios and allow users to adjust simulation parameters.
